OL,3,CWhat is conch blowing? The ancient
OL,4,Critual that could help improve your
OL,5,Csleep
OL,7,FWords by Sanjay Jha, ITV News
OL,8,FJournalist in New Delhi
OL,10,FA centuries-old Indian ritual may hold
OL,11,Fsurprising modern health benefits.
OL,13,FNew research suggests that blowing a
OL,14,Fconch shell - a practice known in
OL,15,FIndia as Shankh blowing - could
OL,16,Fimprove sleep and breathing in people
OL,17,Fwith moderate obstructive sleep apnoea
OL,18,F(OSA), according to research conducted
OL,19,Fby Indian doctors.
