OL,3,CWhat is conch blowing? The ancient
OL,4,Critual that could help improve your
OL,5,Csleep
OL,7,F"This simple practice strengthens the
OL,8,Fbreathing muscles and improves airway
OL,9,Ftone, helping keep passages open
OL,10,Fduring sleep," Dr Krishna K Sharma,
OL,11,Fdirector of pulmonology at Eternal
OL,12,FHospital, Jaipur, and lead researcher
OL,13,Fof the study, told ITV News.
OL,15,F"Many participants slept better,
OL,16,Fsnored less, and felt more energetic
OL,17,Fduring the day."
OL,19,FWhat did the study find?
