OL,7,FThe randomised controlled trial,
OL,8,Fconducted at Eternal Heart Care Centre
OL,9,Fand Research Institute in Rajasthan,
OL,10,Finvolved 30 adults newly diagnosed
OL,11,Fwith moderate OSA.
OL,13,FFourteen participants were trained to
OL,14,Fblow a conch shell for 15 minutes a
OL,15,Fday, five days a week, over six
OL,16,Fmonths. The remaining 16 performed
OL,17,Fdeep breathing exercises as a placebo
OL,18,Fcontrol.
