OL,7,F"For many participants, the experience
OL,8,Fwas both culturally familiar and
OL,9,Fphysically beneficial," Dr Sharma
OL,10,Fadded.
OL,12,F"Several reported not only better
OL,13,Fsleep and reduced snoring, but also a
OL,14,Fsense of calm and improved daytime
OL,15,Fenergy."
OL,17,FWhat is conch blowing and how could it
OL,18,Fhelp with sleep apnea?
