OL,3,CWhat is conch blowing? The ancient
OL,4,Critual that could help improve your
OL,5,Csleep
OL,7,FRooted in Hindu rituals and
OL,8,Fceremonies, conch blowing has been
OL,9,Fpractised in India for centuries. Its
OL,10,Fspiritual symbolism is now being
OL,11,Fexplored for therapeutic potential -
OL,12,Fespecially in treating sleep apnoea, a
OL,13,Fcondition that affects millions
OL,14,Fworldwide and is typically managed
OL,15,Fwith continuous positive airway
OL,16,Fpressure (CPAP) machines.
OL,18,FWhile CPAP is highly effective, many
OL,19,Fpatients - particularly those with
OL,20,Fmilder symptoms - find it
OL,21,Funcomfortable or difficult to maintain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
