OL,12,F"While CPAP remains the gold standard,
OL,13,Fnot everyone can tolerate it," said
OL,14,Fstudy co-author Dr Rajeev Gupta. "For
OL,15,Fsuch patients, conch blowing might
OL,16,Fbecome an accessible and culturally
OL,17,Facceptable option."
OL,19,FThe study, published in ERJ Open
OL,20,FResearch, is already paving the way
OL,21,Ffor broader trials.
