OL,7,FResearchers caution that the findings,
OL,8,Fwhile promising, stem from a small,
OL,9,Fsingle-centre study and must be
OL,10,Fvalidated through larger, multi-centre
OL,11,Fresearch before widespread adoption.
OL,13,FIf confirmed, the ancient sound of the
OL,14,Fconch shell may soon echo not just in
OL,15,Ftemples - but in bedrooms, as a tool
OL,16,Ffor better sleep and respiratory
OL,17,Fhealth.
